    "This calibration step is repeated 2-3 times until rough convergence, when A and B are very similar.",
    "The final steering strength 𝑑 is computed as the average of 𝑑 𝐴 and 𝑑 𝐵.LEARN: Similar to the baseline interface, the user can only control the personalization via prompting (Figure 7c).",
    "The steering strength is updated based on the algorithm described in Equation 1 that accounts for the sentiment of the user's latest message and the preference direction that they wish to steer towards.",
